# --- Source PDFs: kept LOCAL, never committed ---------------------------------
# Theses/dissertations are large binaries and (in part) third-party copyrighted.
# The sources registry (registries/sources.yaml) cites resolvable permalinks /
# DOIs instead of dumping the PDFs into history. See docs/decisions/0002-*.md.
sources/pdf/*
!sources/pdf/README.md

# Internal PAULA analysis notebooks (own primary sources): kept LOCAL and
# registered in registries/sources.yaml so records can cite them, but not
# committed (own unpublished analysis; poorly-diffable .nb blobs). See ADR-0002.
sources/Mathematica/*
!sources/Mathematica/README.md

# --- macOS --------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

